<div id="header">
<h1>LoopInvariant</h1>
</div>
<div id="content">
<div id="preamble">
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p><a href="#">LoopInvariant</a> is an optimization pass for the <a href="SSA">SSA</a>
<a href="IntermediateLanguage">IntermediateLanguage</a>, invoked from <a href="SSASimplify">SSASimplify</a>.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="sect1">
<h2 id="_description">Description</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>This pass removes loop invariant arguments to local loops.</p>
</div>
<div class="listingblock">
<div class="content">
<pre>  loop (x, y)
    ...
  ...
    loop (x, z)
  ...</pre>
</div>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>becomes</p>
</div>
<div class="listingblock">
<div class="content">
<pre>  loop' (x, y)
    loop (y)
  loop (y)
    ...
  ...
    loop (z)
  ...</pre>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
